      "firm_id": "optimistic_7",
      "description": "Looking for an affordable ride or a project you can make your own? This vehicle is priced to reflect its current poor condition \u2014 it has notable mechanical and cosmetic issues that will need attention, so it's best suited for handy buyers, DIY enthusiasts, or those on a very tight budget. The price is set honestly to give you room to invest in repairs. If you're up for the challenge, this could be a rewarding find!",
